        <main>
            <!--Why should you visit Vietnam once in your life?-->
            <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <h2><strong>Why should you visit Vietnam once in your life?</strong></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row mt-4">
                    <div class="col-sm-4 d-flex flex-column">
                        <div class="mb-4" style="padding-right: 50px; padding-top: 25px; text-align: left;">
                            <h4>
                                <strong>Is that you?</strong>
                            </h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Love Adventure?</li>
                                <li>Crave Authentic Culture?</li>
                                <li>Enjoy Delicious Food?</li>
                                <li>Seek Warm Hospitality?</li>
                                <li>Dream of Unforgettable Moments?</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>
                                <strong>No doubt! Come to Vietnam, where your desires come true.</strong> 
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="pt-2 mb-5">
                            <img src="hat.jpeg" alt="Vietnamese Cornical-leaf hat" width="250" height="150">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-8 bg-custom">
                        <h4>People</h4>
                        <p>
                            Vietnam’s people are known for their warmth and hospitality, welcoming travelers with open hearts.
                            The diverse ethnic communities across the country bring a rich variety of traditions and stories, creating a vibrant cultural tapestry.
                        </p>
                        <h4>Cultures</h4>
                        <p>
                            Vietnam’s culture is a blend of ancient traditions and modern influences.
                            From lively festivals to traditional music and art, the country’s heritage is celebrated daily.
                            The bustling markets and serene temples offer a glimpse into the spiritual and artistic soul of Vietnam.
                        </p>
                        <h4>Landscapes</h4>
                        <p>
                            Vietnam’s landscapes range from the terraced rice fields of the northern mountains to the lush valleys and winding rivers of the south.
                            The country’s natural beauty is diverse, with stunning coastal areas, serene rivers, and majestic peaks that captivate every traveler.
                        </p>        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!--Journey Through Vietnam - Card-->
            <div class="full-width-bg">
                <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 mb-5">
                            <h2><strong>Journey Through Vietnam</strong></h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row g-4">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card custom-card">
                                <img src="north-card.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Northern Vietnam">
                                <div class="card-body p-4">
                                    <h5 class="card-title mb-4"><strong>NORTH</strong></h5>
                                    <p class="card-text mb-4">
                                        Experience the essence of Northern Vietnam, where ancient traditions blend seamlessly with the natural beauty of rugged mountains, lush valleys, and iconic terraced rice fields.
                                        The region is known for its vibrant culture, bustling cities, and serene countryside.
                                    </p>
                                    <a href="/explore/north" class="btn custom-btn mt-auto">Explore Now!</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card custom-card">
                                <img src="central-card.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Central Vietnam">
                                <div class="card-body p-4">
                                    <h5 class="card-title mb-4"><strong>CENTRAL</strong></h5>
                                    <p class="card-text mb-4">
                                        Central Vietnam is a land of contrasts, from its stunning coastline to its historic cities.
                                        Here, you will find a rich tapestry of culture, with ancient dynasties, imperial cities, and timeless traditions, all set against a backdrop of pristine beaches and dramatic landscapes.
                                    </p>
                                    <a href="/explore/central" class="btn custom-btn mt-auto">Explore Now!</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card custom-card">
                                <img src="south-card.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Southern Vietnam">
                                <div class="card-body p-4">
                                    <h5 class="card-title mb-4"><strong>SOUTH</strong></h5>
                                    <p class="card-text mb-4">
                                        Southern Vietnam is a dynamic and diverse region, offering everything from the sprawling metropolis of Ho Chi Minh City to the tranquil beauty of the Mekong Delta.
                                        It is a place where modern life coexists with traditional ways, set amidst tropical landscapes and bustling markets.
                                    </p>
                                    <a href="/explore/south" class="btn custom-btn mt-auto">Explore Now!</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!--Vietnam's Essence - Carousel-->
            <div class="container mt-5 mb-5">
                <div class="row mb-5">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <h2><strong>Vietnam’s Essence</strong></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="carousel slide carousel-fade" id="carousel" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="3000">
                    <div class="carousel-indicators">
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="3" aria-label="Slide 4"></button>
                        <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide-to="4" aria-label="Slide 5"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-inner">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <img src="aodaired-crousel.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Ao Dai">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="field-carousel.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Green Rice Terrace Field">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="coffee-carousel.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Filter Coffee">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="food-carousel.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Cuisine">
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img src="Comtam-carousel.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Com Tam">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h3 class="carousel-text">Satisfy Your Senses in Vietnam</h3>
                        <a href="/insights" class="carousel-link">Explore Now!
                            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                        <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                        <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
                    </button>
                </div>    
            </div>

            <!--Never Miss a Moment in Vietnam - Subcription-->
            <div class="subscription-section">
                <div class="container mb-5 mt-5 ">
                    <div class="row mb-4">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <h2><strong>Never Miss a Moment in Vietnam</strong></h2>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
