                                    - Liam S., Sydney, Australia
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="testimonial-box p4 mb-3">
                                <p class="testimonial-text">
                                    "Exploring Vietnam was a dream come true.
                                    The culture, the history, and the experiences are something I'll cherish forever."                                </p>
                                <p class="testimonial-author">
                                    - Sophie M., London, UK
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

